{"type": "article", "id": 54655, "title": "一款像素橡皮擦，也是一组拼装积木｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-26T23:01:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 51378, "name": "Graham & Brown"}, {"id": 32382, "name": "Eastpak"}, {"id": 51379, "name": "Omer Arbel"}, {"id": 51380, "name": "Brian Eno"}, {"id": 51381, "name": "Garcia Tamjidi"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180626223742aylkL31X6I94zENj.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4d4d} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4d4d} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #337ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #337ab7} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s9 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s10 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s11 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4d4d4d} span.s12 {font-kerning: none; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4d4d4d} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>zomozo BLOCKS 像素橡皮擦</h3><p>zomozo BLOCKS 是一款像素橡皮擦，也是一组拼装积木。每一块像素橡皮擦的六个面都可以相互连接， 自由组合，拼接出丰富多彩像素化造型。单块 15*15*15 毫米大小，不会因为过小而不安全，也不会因为过大而拼不出有趣的桌面小物。售价 12 至 66 元，<a href=\"https://weidian.com/item.html?itemID=2557805526\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223825YOqDgxF6hlELKp0m.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262238252eYSsrb1af6t5mGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262238252xbkYnvMJwsZhloU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223824eG38RrOVwKdBjcmW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262238263qZVU5JTX0wdGDto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223825601OzCiRLNSUQrv2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223826mpPR5osETS76hf3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262238269i8d4whjMGvJ3WyU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Raf Simons x Eastpak 2018 AW Collection</h3><p>比利时设计师 Raf Simons 与箱包品牌 Eastpak 推出 2018 秋冬联名系列。灵感源自于 20 世纪中期的高级定制与都市亚文化，并借鉴了 1960 年代的风衣设计，将 Eastpak 经典的包款重新进行诠释。</p><p>新系列包括 5 款设计，其中 RS Classic 在经典双肩包基础上，加上了打褶纹路和不对称的 Oversized 口袋；RS Female 灵感来自传统斗篷，垂褶的结构配上超大容量和翻盖；RS Organized Sling 就在常见单肩背包的基础上，以绳结式背带、钮扣细节和大口袋作为亮点。</p><p>而 RS Sleek Sling 则是 RS Organized Sling 的简化版本，以 Raf Simons Check 格纹呈现；RS Coat Bag 同样受到风衣启发，采用羊毛材质打造，如外套口袋和腰带等经典细节也有体现，定价从 200 到 500 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223912qrZRptYzseXgJS4A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223913if56SUquKYblIZ8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223913oESAINqP3Ftkj92X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223913Z3CTlBVEvJIiQnDy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223913YTiODCAE6ypSHWMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223913x2ejUio8KaYIhXqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GT02 Lamp by Garcia Tamjidi</h3><p>旧金山建筑设计工作室 Garcia Tamjidi 推出了一款名为 GT02 的台灯。它的样式非常简洁，灵感来自于折纸折叠的过程。</p><p>GT02 由激光切割的薄薄的纯铝材质制作而成，凹出有角度的造型。LED 灯泡隐藏在铝板包裹的铝盒内，光线从不同角度散射出来，变得柔和，在点亮的瞬间将灯体变成了一个光之雕塑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223946dfl2QbPEzmHRFk0Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223946ga5J2WVfyxX1jz8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223946BTVYICfOjmG6QapR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262239460hIyYNjdGJt6pBqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223946nueKXpBgyPobqGJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626223946lwnj3MXVahKH4md8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://minimalissimo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalissimo.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Wallpaper Collection with Brian Eno by Graham &amp; Brown</h3><p>英国壁纸制造商 Graham &amp; Brown 青睐有加英国音乐界的标志性人物之一 Brian Eno，为其在美国推出的一系列壁纸提供创意，其中最典型的两款是 Flower Mask Blue 和 Flower Mask Jade。</p><p>Brian Eno 的创作与 Graham &amp; Brown 的品牌特色取个名字开来，为其注入充满活力的色彩和图形元素。它希望 Mask 系列壁纸，能够为用户的家中添入充满戏剧性的美学元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262240201iSXAEWIrkbneafO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224020kPRir6q5dcWNFGZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224021c3pv9mAYG1quMgxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224021GYH0fICh3nXkrlQc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224021vQT5rac6OwG9mC2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224022UqMTO4DPuBmKwkyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Objects by Omer Arbel</h3><p>加拿大灯饰品牌 Bocci 的创意总监 Omer Arbel 最近推出了一个新品牌 OAO Works，将不限于创造任何特定类别的产品。</p><p>31.3 Polygon 玻璃器皿系列，由 31 款玻璃容器组成，是对传统捷克玻璃制造技术的新探索，三种特殊形状的器皿和不同色彩的 31 个产品可以任意组合。84.2 铜网玻璃花瓶的关键词是渐变的色调。64 蜂蜡蜡烛，是蜡和水相互作用形成的有机形状。71.2 首饰系列，则是铜线不见反复浸入带电流的乳化镍溶液中形成的造型，包括戒指、手镯、项链、胸针和耳环等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224049763h51gZdHCyJKcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224049isUKaTWvF3XZepB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224049pDcPzSRmgTdAbLe4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224050ixSfjlewyPF5NDEA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.247656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224050Lh4H9KmXz7Y0tfVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224050ry2QSV9h67431foN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262240503vz19uHxwhsyODlF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://oaoworks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OAO Works</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>RUMTID Collection by IKEA</h3><p>瑞典家具品牌宜家最近接连推出联名企划项目，比如与 Virgil Abloh 合作的 MARKERAD 系列，以及与阿迪达斯和乐高的合作系列等等。最近，宜家又发布了 RUMTID 系列，以 NASA 为灵感来源，确立了“时间”、“小空间”、”水”和“空气”四大主题，设计出前卫之感的家居用品，团队甚至派人专程到 NASA 位于犹他州的火星沙漠研究站作资料搜集，甚至到东京体验胶囊公寓。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224131V0y1f3XTPcBJt8gN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724939\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224131wkxcWP5YNQv1Gtbm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224131q45kT6WDnObFw8rp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806262241312YHfQhbdnZ4Gl1o7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224131VdMRSz0f8PKIT2QE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180626224131DJVauSU08WsTchK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/ikea-nasa-rumtid-collection-urban-small-space-living-06-26-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}